Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,One bear successfully\Neliminated by our trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,We known what you two really\Nare, and this is what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,but also, we loved you\Nfrom the beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.82,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.24,Main,,0,0,0,,so we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I had to have you all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:20.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:24.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sumika. What was it\Nyou wanted to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:10.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs] This letter is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I barely even know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] I guess, I can\Nstart at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The moment I first met Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's gone.\NI can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma gave me that hairpin\Nespecially for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NAre you looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It's yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] I know you probably\Ndon't remember that, but I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.46,Main,,0,0,0,,and it meant the world to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so happy you were there,\Nso happy to have met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NAnd then, there was that storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to protect\Nwhat you cared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You came out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NWe got soaked, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, it was scary, but we ended\Nup having such a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I started feeling\Nso close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Like it was just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The only two people\Nin the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It was heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:48.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I remember everything about\Nthat day, but more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:52.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I will always remember it,\Neven when I'm old and gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "The Moon Girl\Nand the Forest Girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother wrote this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep, it was actually\Nher last book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Since it was never published,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,it's the only copy.\NIt's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Mind if I read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\N"Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:23.24,Main,,0,0,0,,the worlds were divided\Ninto two parts by the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,There was the moon world,\Nand the forest world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.75,Main,,0,0,0,,One day, a moon girl\Naccidentally dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.62,Main,,0,0,0,,her mother's precious pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It fell far down\Ninto the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,A forest girl stumbled\Nupon the pendant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,while she was out walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Surprised by its sparkling star,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,she found herself\Nlooking up at the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.10,Main,,0,0,0,,to see where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,She started to think\Nwhat she could see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,might not be all\Nthere was, and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,'There must be an amazing\Nworld beyond that sky.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the moon girl\Ncouldn't stop wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,about the forest world, and\Nwhat happened to the pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,'Where is Mother's pendant?'\Nshe said. 'I have to go find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,There must be an amazing world\Nbeyond that sky.'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Day after day, the moon girl\Nand the forest girl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:19.09,Main,,0,0,0,,looked at the sky, each one\Ngazing from their own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,At long last, they decided\Nto appeal to Lady Kumaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:27.35,Main,,0,0,0,,for she was the\NGoddess of the Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The moon girl prayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,'Please help me, Lady Kumaria.\NI want to go beyond the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,so I can find\Nmy mother's lost pendant.'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The forest girl prayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,'Please help me, Lady Kumaria.\NI want to go beyond the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,so I can deliver this lost star\Nto the one who dropped it.'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,'I am sorry, but you\Nmay not,' said Kumaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,'For the two worlds\Nhave been severed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wanting to cross that\Nseverance is pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,and pride, as you know,\Nis a grave sin.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, they prayed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,'Please help us, we still want\Nto go beyond the sky.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Reluctantly,\NKumaria answered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,'There is one way\Nto make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,In the center of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:22.69,Main,,0,0,0,,is a place called\Nthe Door to Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If your love is true, your\Nfriend will be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll find her on the\Nother side of that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:33.54,Main,,0,0,0,,When you see her,\Ngive her a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:37.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Do that, and your wish\Nshall come true.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:41.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Kumaria asked the\Ntwo girls a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,'Is your love the real thing?'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, she laid down\Na ladder for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:52.26,Main,,0,0,0,,connecting the two worlds\Ntogether once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,They climbed the ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,until finally arriving\Nat the center of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,There they found a single,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,vast mirror standing\Nlike a wall in their path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:09.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Each girl saw her own\Nreflection in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,They heard Kumaria's voice say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,'Now, your friend is waiting\Njust on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,of that very door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,If you smash the 'you'\Nin the mirror to bits,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,if you tear yourself apart, she\Nshall grant you a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,But beware, this may\Ncost you your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I will ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:37.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?'
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,The girls stared at themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:42.19,Main,,0,0,0,,in the mirror for\Na very long time."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No, the story\Ndoesn't have an ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear killed Mom. She never\Ngot the chance to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.20,Main,,0,0,0,,How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what would you do\Nif it was about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NUh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, that part in the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you risk your life\Nin order to break the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure.\NLemme think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI would break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NWha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd shoot my reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd shoot because\NI would do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.65,Main,,0,0,0,,to prove my love was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NIn that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I decided I wouldn't\Nback down on love, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,...I would do anything\Nto prove my love, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, ladies, it's time to decide\Non the next evil to exclude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KATYUSHA]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, ladies.\NI have bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems we have a traitor\Namong our ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki was the one\Nset up to be the next evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\Nbefore we can target her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,we must first\Nexclude the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she agrees.\NRight, Sumika Izumino?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NKureha, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I jumped into the storm myself,\Nand I did it willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] At the time, I thought\Nif I could prove my love,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:59.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Even heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But then, I realized\NI was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be me the\NInvisible Storm would break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It would wind up being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.67,Main,,0,0,0,,The one I care about most.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NGood, you wrote the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I can take it now. That way I'll\Nbe ready to give it to Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NAbout the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you mind\Nholding off a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to wait until we\Ncelebrate Kureha's birthday here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.95,Main,,0,0,0,,at the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever.\NJust don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to be\NKureha's new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the only way we can make\Nsure the storm will pass her by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NI can't stop the storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,but I can protect Kureha\Nas long as I'm her new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I know it puts you\Nin a terrible position,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:05.68,Main,,0,0,0,,but we have no other choice\Nif we want to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I still think I should do it.\NDeliver the letter, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NNo. Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the last love\NI ever get to give her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,so it has to be done right.\NIt has to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] Kureha, this will\Nbe my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Because, I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I promise to never\Nback down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NI owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You told me the truth\Nabout Ginko and Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That they were bears\Ndisguised as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Because of you, I got\Nto set a trap in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,We know what you are,\Nand this is what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NBear Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA groans, yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nthat stupid bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knew she'd have\Na trick up her sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--[footstep]\N--Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.28,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The plan is still going\Noff without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sumika's death was\Ndefinitely unexpected,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:48.08,Main,,0,0,0,,but your idea of using it\Nwas inspired. Pure genius. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow it'll finally be\NKureha Tsubaki's birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,and I think we'll\Nreally enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone,\Nfor your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] I wonder where\Nthey could've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I was planning\Nto apologize, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:23.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl. Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NOh, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, sniffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang it. Stupid Kaoru Harishima.\NIt doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,How did she even know\Nwe were bears?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NReia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't help but be reminded of\Nthe day I swore my love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, it's your\Ndaughter's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:56.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she'll get from\Nher friend on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,So that it's perfect,\Nsince it's my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:14.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika, I promise\Nto accept your gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.96,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'll do\Nwhat you asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NHey, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the day\Nof the entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NPummeled by the cold wind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.47,Main,,0,0,0,,that scattered\Nthe cherry blossoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,a girl searched for something,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.47,Main,,0,0,0,,but she couldn't\Nseem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NI felt bad for Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,No one helped her\Nlook for it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Although, why would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It was just some cheap hairpin,\Nnothing to get upset about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But you, you're not\Nlike the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA] Tell me something.\NWhy haven't you lost hope, yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.54,Main,,0,0,0,,The world is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You've lost things,\Nhad them taken from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you become invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Well... I think it's\Nbecause I don't forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand\Nwhat that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] It means, as long\Nas you don't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll never, ever be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,And if you don't\Ngive up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you if you\Nlose something,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,you won't be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.19,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a letter from Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,She gave it to me\Nnot too long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,This-This is my\Nbirthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to read it\Nat the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,So, Kureha, it means a lot\Nthat you're giving us a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,to make amends for\Nall this. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm super excited about\Nyour birthday party, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no need\Nto thank me, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NEspecially considering your love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:51.72,Main,,0,0,0,,is about to be utterly destroyed\Nby the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Yuri ga aku. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl! Ginko! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lulu's so happy, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What a relief!\NThat was terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu was so worried! She didn't\Nknow what she'd do if you died!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu did everything\Nshe could think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She carried you\Nall the way to here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.74,Main,,0,0,0,,and stayed up the whole night\Ntaking care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Today is Kureha's\Nbirthday! Growl, growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:18.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I said, today is\NKureha's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.04,Main,,0,0,0,,--[phone ringing]\N--[BOTH] Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a challenge from\Nthe Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro,\Nif your love is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,you need to get\Nto the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The moon girl is there right\Nnow awaiting for your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Do I know a "moon girl"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is give\Nyourself over to the flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,only then will\Nyour love be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha! Are you\Ntrying to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,the moon girl is\Nsupposed to be Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the Promise Kiss\Nwill come to pass, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We shall see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,For that is sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.06,Main,,0,0,0,,On your birthday, Kureha,\Nwe wish you well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NHappy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You told Sumika you'd read\Nher letter right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] "Kureha. The girl\Nstanding in front of you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,...is your new friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NExactly what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious\Nwhen you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That's Sumika's\Nbreak-up letter to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Seems she's trying\Nto give you a gift, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Her final present for you was to\Nmake sure you had a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,One that wasn't her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,But we have no intention
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,of making friends with you,\NKureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine\Nit feels very good
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.03,Main,,0,0,0,,to realize you\Nwere both tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We were tricked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NThat's right! Surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I was the one who had\NSumika write the letter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,to you in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA] Her death\Nscrewed up the original plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,yet, fortunately,\Nwe got to use that letter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,to punish the real evil anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl who refuses\Nto follow social cues.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.59,Main,,0,0,0,,In order to wish you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.17,Main,,0,0,0,,the happiest of birthdays,\NKureha Tsubaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,this is a little something\Nspecial from Us to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:39.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NHappy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The time has come for Us\Nto exclude the evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NExclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, does evil get\Nto have any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NNo friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, does evil get crushed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Crushed by the Invisible\NStorm as punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NCrushed as punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:10.79,Main,,0,0,0,,She's excluded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:13.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Good job, ladies. Kureha Tsubaki\Njust snapped like a twig!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NYay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B]\NWe did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NTragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't get any new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.76,Main,,0,0,0,,On top of that,\Nyou'll never be able to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino's final gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a pity. At least now\Nyou know the emotion of love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,is powerless and pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,No use for this anymore. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Sumika wrote that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NSuch a beautiful smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to always\Nsmile like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Like a flower. That's my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's funny. Even if I had to\Nwatch you from a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I would be happy\Njust to see that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, it's Sumika's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.21,Main,,0,0,0,,She gave to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWha--? Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone,\Nlooks like the party's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't. I'll never\Nback down on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:33.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu would have killed you\Nif you'd really died this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a dummy, too! She did it\Nbecause she loves you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,She wha--? She loves me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:49.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko loves you so much\Nlook at what she's done for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:58.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't waste her love!\NPlease, don't waste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] "Kureha, the girl\Nstanding in front of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,is your new friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Is this for real?\NShe's my new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] I think\NI got here a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm gonna have\Nto fix this place fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:02.48,Main,,0,0,0,,The flowerbed has to be\Npacked full of flowers again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,before Kureha's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NWell, good morning, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.61,0:24:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,0:24:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NSuch a lovely morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm practically starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.63,0:24:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NMitsuko, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.59,0:24:21.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.92,0:24:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[thud]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.30,0:24:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NGrowl, growl, chomp, chomp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.55,0:24:27.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl,growl, chomp, chomp.\NGrowl-growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] That day,\NI committed a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I am a... criminal bear.
